title: Episode 19: Eye Movement Desensitization and Reprocessing: an interview with Jamie O’Neil
description:
Want to learn more about EMDR? Listen to this interview with Jamie O’Neil who explains how EMDR works. Turns out it’s about a lot more than just eye movements. Learn more about Bilateral Stimulation...

Show notes and more available at http://www.thepsychfiles.com
